content: A sudden rush of nostalgia! The only problem is that it is not tailored for the new screen resolutions. It zooms the game to fill in the screen space cutting off the top and bottom of the game. Its a paid game and I don't regret buying this age old memorable game. The only disappointment is that when the developers remastered the game, I thought they would consider the screen resolution to be updated too. Hope they fix it soon or give an option to change how we fill the screen.
